message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with music and drumming, which falls under the category of sound and music computing. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper uses Seq2Seq and recurrent VIB models, cs.AI (artificial intelligence) as the paper explores the creative potential of these models, cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper adapts an approach from the GAN literature, and cs.CL (computation and language) as the paper deals with translating abstract musical ideas into expressive performances.
